## How to Play
- **WASD / Arrow Keys** — Move your character
- **Space / Click** — Attack (melee swing)
- **Space near NPC** — Talk to NPCs
- **E** — Interact / Pick up items
- **1-6** — Use inventory items
- **M** — Toggle minimap
- **P** — Pause
- **I** — Toggle inventory view

## Quest
